aVThis is the environment that's being created
p167
aVby cyber weapons today,
p168
aVand historically it was the environment in Europe
p169
aVat the onset of World War I.
p170
aVSo cyber weapons
p171
aVare dangerous by nature,
p172
aVbut in addition, they're emerging
p173
aVin a much more unstable environment.
p174
aa(lp175
VIf you remember the Cold War,
p176
aVit was a very hard game,
p177
aVbut a stable one played only by two players,
p178
aVwhich allowed for some coordination between the two superpowers.
p179
aVToday we're moving to a multipolar world
p180
aVin which coordination is much more complicated,
p181
aVas we have seen at Copenhagen.
